name: The Blood Brothers by Raine Wilder

metadata.name: ONE CALL
metadata.description:
The Blood Brothers are two day walker vampires who are bound to doing the Earthly dirty deeds of the Devil.

This time, The Blood Brothers find themselves in jail, making their ONE CALL. Who are they calling? The only one who can get them out...

This is the first in a series of editions to come. Every holder of ONE CALL will get an airdrop of the next edition in the series of The Blood Brothers.
